CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in New Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 5, 1967, pg. 14 reads: "Five Generations - Little Latisha Eloise Henderson (seated on lap of great-great grandmother, Mrs. Mary Rowland) made the fifth generation represented in family pictured here. On Mrs. Rowland's left is her daughter Mrs. Jeannette Henderson, on the right is Mrs. Henderson's daughter Mrs. Eloise Grace of Philadelphia. In the rear are Mrs. Grace's son Preston and his wife Mildred Henderson.  The reunion took place at Mrs. Rowland's home on Elmore Sq., Pittsburgh. - Harris photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of Rowland - Henderson family, from left, front row: Jeannette Henderson, Latisha Eloise Henderson, held by Mary Rowland, and Eloise Grace; back row: Preston Henderson and Mildred Henderson, posed in home of Mary Rowland, Elmore Square
